com.b2international.commons

Class ExplicitFirstOrdering<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.collect.Ordering<T>
      • com.b2international.commons.ExplicitFirstOrdering<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparator<T>

    public class ExplicitFirstOrdering<T>
extends com.google.common.collect.Ordering<T>
implements Serializable
    An ordering that compares objects according to a given order. If a compared object is not among the given elements, it will be placed last in the order.
